latestIgtvVideos.title: #NeutrogenaPartner Get Ready With Me ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I take my skincare seriously, so I’m always looking for healthy ingredients in my makeup. Wearing the @Neutrogena Healthy Skin Liquid Foundation paired with their Healthy Skin Brightening Eye Perfecter for lightweight and non greasy coverage with SPF 20. SPF is a key ingredient for me especially since i’m out in the sun a lot to shoot and sunburns aren’t cute. I’ve had it for a couple weeks now and it’s already become one of my go-to’s 💕

You can find it at @CVS_beauty #CVSbeauty #NeutrogenaMakeup // Heads up, if you Spend $30, get a $10 Gift Card through Fandango!

Music by @joakimkarudmusic
